    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid shape, runs smoothly, and has been well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. I\u2019m looking for a quick, easy sale to help boost my seller profile, so I've priced it to move! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great new home!",
      "price": 29500.0,
