    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, providing a tactile connection to the M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity, including documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. It sits on factory Style 67 forged wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. While the finish shows light patina from spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A driver-centric machine with all essential preventative maintenance addressed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
