    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road wear consistent with careful, regular use. Inside, the smoke-free leather cabin remains supple and exceptionally clean, featuring a premium sound system and a panoramic sunroof that functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; I have stayed ahead of all scheduled maintenance, and the tires have significant tread remaining. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a confident, quiet ride. This is a dependable, high-quality car that has been cared for with a detail-oriented eye, now ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
