    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies consistent maintenance and reliable performance. Meticulously curated to meet our professional standards, this unit offers a sophisticated driving experience characterized by mechanical integrity and a well-preserved interior. This offering represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning motorist seeking a dependable, high-caliber vehicle that balances performance with long-term value. Inspections are welcomed to confirm the superior standard of this automotive investment.",
      "price": 32800.0,
