    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and she's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-loved, so you can expect a smooth ride from day one. It\u2019s perfect if you're looking for something dependable that still looks great on the road. I've taken care of all the basics, so it's ready for your next adventure! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
