    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system overhaul. The 6-speed manual transmission provides precise gear selection, sending power through a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is enhanced by Bilstein dampers, ensuring sharp turn-in and controlled damping. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the powertrain remains robust and the chassis is rigid, offering the visceral feedback expected of a true M-division product.",
